It was amazing careful analysis was done and no pain during procedure.

A friendly doctor who spends enough time to explain the issue. She provides appointment based on our convenient time even on Sundays..  I would strongly recommend her for people who are afraid of procedures.. she has a way of convincing the patients to co-operate well for the treatment.

I went to Dr.Logarani for sensitivity in one of my wisdom teeth. The doctor diagnosed a decay and treated it with filling after cleaning. I don’t have any issues after the treatment. The doctor clearly explained me the diagnosis and the treatment answering questions clearly. Based on her insights, I chose to take up filling instead of a root canal. The doctor is very approachable and friendly throughout the interactions. My parents also got treated with her for tooth extraction and root canal treatment and they are doing better now. I would definitely recommend her for dental consultations.

Dr Logarani was professional to keep the facts in assertive manner.. Gave a detailed walk through in layman terms without any medical jargons.Gave a comprehensive perspective of after effects and anticipated issues if any . Kept the patient aware to take appropriate decisions as per necessity and severity.Would strongly recommend. Even in case of any requirements of a second opinion this is the place to be for clearing ambiguities.Thanks for the empathy which is scarce offlate in a highly manipulative world.Same applies to Dr Dhanraj as well. Beyond doctors, simple and humble individuals, rest assured you are in safe hands.Thanks once again for providing your service on a Newyear eve, amid pandemic.God bless._/\_
